Achilles was a famous greek warrior.When Achilles was a child his mother dipped him in the river Stynx 
so his whole body became very strong,his body was as strong as a rock but his heel was the only part 
which was weak.Achilles was trained by his Mother. He always listened to his Mother but once he wanted to
go to war and his mother advised against it.For the first time he neglected Mother's warning and went to war
The war lasted for 10 years and Achilles lost many near and dear ones in the war. In the last year of the war 
Achilles was killed by an arrow which hit him in the heel. 